## LOYIHA

SavdoAI — O'zbekiston savdogarlari uchun AI-powered savdo boshqaruv tizimi.
Telegram bot + FastAPI REST API + Next.js web + Android printer app.
20,000+ foydalanuvchi, PostgreSQL RLS izolyatsiya.
GitHub: https://github.com/Mashrab1993/savdoai
Railway: f9933a08 (web=API, savdoai=bot, savdoai-web=Next.js)

## ARXITEKTURA

services/api/main.py — 54 endpoint (2489 qator)
services/api/routes/ — 11 modul, 60 endpoint (tovarlar, klientlar, hisobotlar, kassa, faktura, monitoring, printer, filial, yangi, websocket)
services/bot/main.py — 55+ buyruq (1014 qator)
services/bot/handlers/ — 13 modul (commands, savdo, matn, callbacks, hujjat, excel_chat, narx, shogird, barcode, jobs, yangi, yordam)
services/bot/db.py — DB operatsiyalar (1346 qator)
services/web/ — Next.js 15, 21 sahifa, React + Tailwind + shadcn/ui
services/worker/tasks.py — 8 Celery task
services/cognitive/ — Claude + Gemini AI engine
shared/services/ — 55 biznes modul (ledger, loyalty, kpi, ai_advisor, excel_chat, demand_forecast...)
shared/database/schema.sql — 40 jadval, 54 index, 35+ RLS
android/ — Kotlin ESC/POS Bluetooth printer app
tests/ — 1564+ test, 21 fayl

## RAILWAY TOPOLOGIYA (KRITIK!)

web = FastAPI API (NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL shu yerga!)
savdoai = Telegram Bot (API EMAS!)
savdoai-web = Next.js Frontend

## ENDPOINT PATTERN

@router.post("/endpoint", tags=["Guruh"])
async def endpoint(data: Sorov, uid: int = Depends(get_uid)):
    async with rls_conn(uid) as c:
        row = await c.fetchrow("INSERT INTO ... VALUES ($1,$2) RETURNING id, nomi", uid, data.nomi)
    return dict(row)

