## DB

40 jadval, RLS: current_uid() → user_id policy
Istisnolar: shogirdlar/xarajatlar/xarajat_kategoriyalar → admin_uid

## 🚫 TAQIQLANGAN (14 qoida)

1. SELECT * yozma
2. RETURNING * yozma
3. except: (bare) yozma — except Exception: ishlat
4. f"%{term}%" yozma — like_escape() ishlat
5. SET qoldiq = $2 (absolyut) yozma
6. get_pool() biznes queryda ishlatma — rls_conn(uid) ishlat
7. parol_hash ni response da qaytarma
8. bot URL ni NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL ga qo'yma
9. Test sonini 1564 dan kamaytirma
10. TypeScript xato qoldirma
11. __import__("os") ishlatma — import os yoz
12. hashlib.md5() tizim hashda ishlatma — sha256 ishlat
13. asyncio.get_event_loop() ishlatma — asyncio.run() ishlat
14. Duplikat endpoint yaratma (main.py + routes/)
